\c 16
\s UNkulunkulu unika amaIsrayeli imana
\p
\v 1 Basebesuka eElimi\x + Nani 33.10,11.\x*, lenhlangano yonke yabantwana bakoIsrayeli yafika enkangala yeSini, ephakathi kweElimi leSinayi, ngosuku lwetshumi lanhlanu lwenyanga yesibili emva kokuphuma kwabo elizweni leGibhithe.
\v 2 Lenhlangano yonke yabantwana bakoIsrayeli yakhonona imelana loMozisi loAroni\x + 15.24; 17.3. 1 Kor. 10.10.\x* enkangala.
\v 3 Abantwana bakoIsrayeli basebesithi kubo: Kungathi ngabe safa ngesandla seN\nd kosi\nd* elizweni leGibhithe lapho sasihlezi embizeni zenyama, lapho sadla isinkwa sasutha\x + Nani 11.4,5.\x*; ngoba lisikhuphele kulinkangala ukuze libulale lelibandla lonke ngendlala.
\p
\v 4 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuMozisi: Khangela, ngizalinisela isinkwa sivela emazulwini\x + Hlab. 78.24,25; 105.40. Joha. 6.31,32,49,58. 1 Kor. 10.3.\x*; labantu bazaphuma ukubutha isabelo sosuku ngosuku lwaso, ukuze ngibalinge\x + 15.25.\x* ukuthi bazahamba ngomlayo wami yini kumbe hayi.
\v 5 Kuzakuthi-ke ngosuku lwesithupha bazalungisa lokho abakulethileyo, njalo kuzabe kuphindwe kabili kulokho abakubuthayo insuku ngensuku\x + 16.22. Levi 25.21.\x*.
\v 6 UMozisi loAroni basebesithi kubo bonke abantwana bakoIsrayeli: Kusihlwa\x + 16.12,13.\x*, khona lizakwazi ukuthi iN\nd kosi\nd* ilikhuphile elizweni leGibhithe\x + 6.7. Nani 16.28,29,30.\x*;
\v 7 njalo kusisa, khona lizabona inkazimulo yeN\nd kosi\x + 16.10.\x*\nd*, ngoba izwile ukukhonona kwenu limelene leN\nd kosi\nd*. Thina-ke siyini ukuthi lisikhononele\x + 16.8. Nani 16.11.\x*?
\v 8 UMozisi wasesithi: Lapho iN\nd kosi\nd* ilinika inyama yokudla kusihlwa, lesinkwa ekuseni, ukuze lisuthe, \add ku\add*ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* izwile ukukhonona kwenu elikukhonona limelene layo. Ngoba thina siyini? Ukukhonona kwenu kakumelananga lathi, kodwa kumelene leN\nd kosi\x + 1 Sam. 8.7.\x*\nd*.
\p
\v 9 UMozisi wasesithi kuAroni\x + 4.14-16.\x*: Tshono kunhlangano yonke yabantwana bakoIsrayeli \add uthi\add*: Sondelani phambi kweN\nd kosi\x + Nani 16.16.\x*\nd*, ngoba izwile ukukhonona kwenu.
\v 10 Kwasekusithi uAroni esakhuluma kunhlangano yonke yabantwana bakoIsrayeli, bakhangela ngasenkangala, khangela-ke, inkazimulo yeN\nd kosi\nd* yabonakala eyezini\x + 16.7. 13.21; 14.24. Nani 16.19. 1 Kho. 8.10,11.\x*.
\p
\v 11 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kuMozisi isithi:
\v 12 Sengizwile ukukhonona kwabantwana bakoIsrayeli\x + 16.8.\x*; batshele uthi: Kusihlwa lizakudla inyama\x + 16.8.\x*, lekuseni lisuthe isinkwa\x + 16.7.\x*, njalo lizakwazi ukuthi ngiyiN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu.
\v 13 Kwasekusithi ntambama kwenyuka izagwaca, zasibekela inkamba; lakusisa kwakulomlalela wamazolo uzingelezele inkamba.
\v 14 Kwathi umlalela wamazolo usuwenyukile, khangela-ke, phezu kobuso benkangala into eyisigaqa encinyane, incinyane njengongqwaqwane emhlabathini\x + Nani 11.9.\x*.
\v 15 Kwathi abantwana bakoIsrayeli be\add zi\add*bona bathi omunye komunye: Kuyini lokhu? Ngoba babengazi ukuthi kuyini. UMozisi wasesithi kubo: Kuyisinkwa iN\nd kosi\nd* elinike sona ukuze lidle\x + 16.4. Dute. 8.3. Neh. 9.15.\x*.
\v 16 Le yinto iN\nd kosi\nd* elilaye ngayo \add yathi\add*: Ngulowo lalowo kabuthe kuyo okulingene ukudla kwakhe\x + 16:18,21; 12.4.\x*, \w i-omeri\w** ngekhanda, njengenani lemiphefumulo yenu, ngulowo uzathathela abasethenteni lakhe.
\v 17 Abantwana bakoIsrayeli basebesenza njalo, babutha, omunye okunengi lomunye okulutshwana.
\v 18 Sebelinganise \w nge-omeri\w**\x + 16.36.\x*, lowo owayebuthe okunengi kabanga lokusalayo, lowayebuthe okulutshwana kaswelanga\x + 2 Kor. 8.15.\x*; babutha, ngulowo lalowo okulingene ukudla kwakhe\x + 16.16.\x*.
\v 19 UMozisi wasesithi kubo: Kakungabi lamuntu otshiya kukho kuze kube sekuseni.
\v 20 Kodwa kabamlalelanga uMozisi; kodwa abanye batshiya kukho kwaze kwaba sekuseni, kwasekuphethuza impethu, kwaba levumba. Ngakho uMozisi wabathukuthelela.
\v 21 Bakubutha ukusa ngokusa, ngulowo lalowo okulingene ukudla kwakhe; lapho ilanga selitshisa, kwancibilika.
\p
\v 22 Kwasekusithi ngosuku lwesithupha babutha isinkwa esiphindwe kabili, \w ama-omeri\w** amabili ngamunye. Njalo zonke izinduna zenhlangano zeza zamtshela uMozisi.
\v 23 Wasesithi kuzo: Lokhu yikho iN\nd kosi\nd* ekutshiloyo: Kusasa yikuphumula, isabatha elingcwele leN\nd kosi\x + Gen. 2.3. Eks. 20.8; 31.14-17; 35.2,3. Levi 23.3. Gen. 29.27.\x*\nd*. Bhakani elizakubhaka, lipheke elizakupheka, konke lokho okuseleyo lizibekele kugcinwe kuze kube sekuseni.
\v 24 Basebekubeka kwaze kwaba sekuseni njengokulaya kukaMozisi. Njalo kakubanga levumba, kwakungelampethu kukho\x + 16.20.\x*.
\v 25 UMozisi wasesithi: Dlanini lokhu lamuhla, ngoba lamuhla kulisabatha leN\nd kosi\nd*; lamuhla kaliyikukuthola egangeni.
\v 26 Lizakubutha insuku eziyisithupha; kodwa ngosuku lwesikhombisa, isabatha, kakuyikuba khona kulo.
\p
\v 27 Kwasekusithi ngosuku lwesikhombisa \add abanye\add* babantu baphuma ukubutha, kodwa kaba\add ku\add*tholanga.
\v 28 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuMozisi: Koze kube nini lisala ukugcina imilayo yami lemithetho yami?
\v 29 Bonani, ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* ilinikile isabatha, ngakho ilinika ngosuku lwesithupha isinkwa sensuku ezimbili; hlalani kube ngulowo lalowo endaweni yakhe, kakungaphumi muntu endaweni yakhe ngosuku lwesikhombisa\x + Josh. 5.8. Jobe 40.12.\x*.
\v 30 Ngakho abantu baphumula ngosuku lwesikhombisa.
\v 31 Indlu yakoIsrayeli yasibiza ibizo lakho \add ngokuthi\add* yimana\x + 16.15.\x*; njalo kwakunjengenhlanyelo \w yekhoriyanderi\w** emhlophe, lokunambitheka kwayo kwakunjengezinkwana eziyizipatalala eziloluju\x + Nani 11.7,8.\x*.
\p
\v 32 UMozisi wasesithi: Le yinto iN\nd kosi\nd* elaye ngayo \add ukuthi\add*: Gcwalisani i-omeri ngayo igcinelwe izizukulwana zenu, ukuze zibone isinkwa engalinika sona ukuthi lidle enkangala ekulikhupheni kwami elizweni leGibhithe.
\v 33 UMozisi wasesithi kuAroni: Thatha inqayi eyodwa, ufake kuyo \w i-omeri\w** eligcwele imana, uyibeke phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*, igcinelwe izizukulwana zenu\x + Heb. 9.4.\x*.
\v 34 Njengokulaya kweN\nd kosi\nd* kuMozisi, uAroni wayibeka phambi kobufakazi ukuze igcinwe\x + 25.16,21; 26.33,34; 27.21; 30.6,26,36; Dute. 10.5. 2 Kho. 11.12.\x*.
\v 35 Abantwana bakoIsrayeli-ke badla imana iminyaka engamatshumi amane\x + Dute. 8.2,3. Neh. 9.15,20,21.\x* baze bafika elizweni elakhiweyo\x + Josh. 5.12.\x*. Badla imana baze bafika emngceleni welizwe leKhanani.
\v 36 I-\w omeri-ke\w** ingokwetshumi \w kwe-efa\w**\x + Levi 5.11; 6.20.\x*.
